  m_Name: Fire Sword
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WeaponItemData
  itemName: Fire sword
  description: 'A blade tempered in molten core. Each swing leaves embers in its
    wake, and its wielder commands both a blazing rush and orbiting flames.

    <b><color=#8E44AD>[E]</color></b>
    Fire Slash: Lunges forward with a searing arc that burns enemies over time.

    <b><color=#8E44AD>[Q]</color></b>
    Inferno Burst: Launches a fire wave ahead while three fireballs orbit behind
    you, homing onto nearby foes.'
